description.content:
Hi, I will help you to turn your next website into a brand using my expertise. 


I am a full-time freelance Front-End Web Developer with the qualification of Education in this field. I Completed my BSc. in CSE and MSc. in IIT. I have completed more than 300+ projects on Fiverr and also have a strong portfolio with 7 years of experience, I will design with your ideas, and concepts, and also with my knowledge.  


What will you get from me? 

  • Well-commented and documented code
  • Responsive Landing Page
  • Pure Wordpress or HTML Landing Page 
  • Pixel Perfect Design 
  • Cross-browser compatibility
  • SEO-optimized code
  • Fully Custom Website


What do I need from you to start building the website?

  • Sample, references, figma/psd, or any concepts/ideas
  • Domain & Hosting - if you have
  • The contents that you will want on your websites, such as - Images, Texts and layouts

 

The technologies that I will use usually: 

  • HTML for Markup
  • Bootstrap For CSS Layout
  • CSS for animation/transition
  • JavaScript for interaction and effects
  • Jquery library
  • PHP - MySQL


Want to know more about my skills and see some of my previous work, then you may go with these links:

  • https://tanjilrahman.xyz/
  • https://github.com/tanjilrahman321

questionsAndAnswers.question: What your need to start order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Give me any kind of file for HTML Conversion like - PSD, XD, Sketch, Figma, PDF, Docx, Images, Reference website or any idea about your web page.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If I need any changes, will you do it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah! you can always ask for any edits or modifications after I deliver the landing page files.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you use any Software for html css conversion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, all codes are hand coded and will be well documented.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I get a pixel-perfect Design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah, get a pixel-perfect design with responsiveness.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you need website logo and images/text?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, send me the logo and images/text or docs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you have any sample site or previous work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, just knock me for free discussion, I will give you my portfolio link or some sample website link.
